This paper is primarily focused on image cropping, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel model that uses deep neural networks for learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with refining feature maps and view sampling, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
